                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row"></div>
                <hr />

                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-3">
                    <p class="mb-0">Referal link:</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-9 d-flex">
                    <p
